        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "See: http:\/\/issues.ez.no\/IssueView.php?Id=15085:\n\nPass a relative path to Zend_Search_Lucene::create(), which is the location of the Lucene index. During shutdown the destructor of a class in Zend Lucene will try to write out the index if it was modified. Since PHP resets the current working directory to \/ on some SAPIs (e.g. apache) writing the index will fail because the relative path now points to a different location. Thus Zend Lucene throws an Exception without a stack frame because it took place during shutdown.\n"
        },
